data.description: Perfect Open Floor Plan Featuring 5 Bedrooms & 3 Full Baths. This Split Bedroom Plan has a Huge Master Bedroom with Trey Ceiling, Crown Molding and Boasts a Master En-Suite with Garden Tub, Separate 5-foot Shower, Double Vanities with Granite Countertops, 2 Walk-in closets and Separate Linen Closet. Kitchen has Granite Countertops and Features a Large Island overlooking Living Room, Stainless Steel Appliance. Eat-In/Dining Room.  The Spacious Living Room has Double Trey Ceilings with Crown Molding and Ceiling Fan.  You’ll find 3 Bedrooms in a Separate Wing with a Full Bath featuring Double Vanities.  5Th Bedroom is Separate and has the 3rd Full Bath right across from it, perfect for Guest Room or Home Office Space. Large Fenced Back Yard with a Screened-In Back Patio and Outside Deck Area.  Fabulous Fairhope Location, Within Walking Distance to School and Soccer Fields.
